\Psionic{Shadow Walk, Psionic}{psionic shadow walk}
{Psychometabolism (Shadow)}
{
	\textbf{Level:}
	Nomad 3\\
	\textbf{Manifesting Time:}
	1 mental action\\
	\textbf{Range:}
	240 meters\\
	\textbf{Target:}
	You\\
	\textbf{Saving Throw:}
	None\\
	\textbf{Cost:}
	15 power points\\
	\textbf{Maintenance Cost:}
	None (Instantaneous)\\
	% \textbf{Critical Success:}
	% You may travel to any shadow within 3 km.\\
	% \textbf{Critical Failure:}
	% You succeed on a Will save, or summon 1d4 shadows from your own shadow to attack you.\\
}
{
	As the \spell{shadow walk} spell, except as noted here.

	This power only works if you can see the shadow you are teleporting to.

	\textit{Augment:} If you spend 15 additional power points, you can travel blindly to a shadow you cannot see.
}